Package fang2.transformers

Class SpinAccelerationTransformer

java.lang.Object
fang2.core.TransformerAdapter
fang2.transformers.SpinTransformer
fang2.transformers.SpinAccelerationTransformer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Transformer
public class SpinAccelerationTransformer extends SpinTransformer
A "spinner" TransformerAdapter. This transformer turns the sprite according to a changing angular velocity. Acceleration is constant, held in the angular acceleration field. The field is available in all angle types supported by fang2.
